Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,並且使得所有的攻擊幾乎無效這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這是因為λ-Driver這個裝置產生運作的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是和相良士官的 Arbalest(強弩兵)所搭載的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,幾乎是完全相同的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,少校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事　威巴士官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,λ-Driver是什麼東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,關於這點　有請上校來進行說明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因為被設定為機密內容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以無法對大家進行詳細的說明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這裡告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂λ-Driver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是被暫定為現斥力場生成系統的一種裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯..也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,簡單來說...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是把人的想像直接轉換成為物理力量的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,例如　將子彈給反彈回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是破壞目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你們認為我是在開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　請問...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是　毛士官長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此萬能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼宗介很少使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我從來沒有親眼見過宗介使用過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,其實...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這是這個裝置的效果被認為不安定的主要原因之一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,就是會對人類的意識產生反應這點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就像剛才所提到的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是每次在發動力量的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都需要有非常強烈的集中力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,集中力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,比方說　只有在攸關生死的極限狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,才能發揮出來的那一類東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在沒有達到那種程度的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就會以啞炮而結束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是之前與我方交戰的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺上已經可以恣意的操縱它了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那些傢伙為什麼可以做到...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不能確定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,應該是受過了相當程度的訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,亦或是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,使用了某種藥物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,以人工方式引發類似那樣的狀態吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.55,0:04:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是　楊伍長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Arbalest(強弩兵) 之外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有搭載著λ-Driver 的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然在秘銀內部...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也希望能進行該裝置的研究和開發
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是由於各種的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,現階段而言仍然是毫無頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只有相良士官可以戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也並非是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在沒有λ-Driver的情況下交戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,必須有較大損傷的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在座的各位請稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,λ-Driver 的應對措施　目前還在研究當中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦有了報告　便會通知大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,以上　解散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,從相良士官那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,傳來有關幽靈的報告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,多少我也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,護衛任務嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,在目前不知道窺視著小要的對手情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,只讓相良君與幽靈兩人保護身為 傾聽者(Whispered)  的她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,從大局上看來可能還是太單薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是能派遣的人員也是受到限制的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖這麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也不能再將 傾聽者(Whispered)  所擁有的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,黑科技 交給那些人...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,傾聽者(Whispered) ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也好　小要也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒有聽到那種聲音的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,應該可以作為一個普通的女孩生活下去吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早安啊　小要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　早安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吶　吶　看看唷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我發現一個有趣的網站
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,咦咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呀啊啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,唔...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,測驗卷的資料...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我三天的辛苦成果啊　嗚嗚嗚...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,屋頂上好像有什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　是真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好大呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊..啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,小要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看看吧　這個雷達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這一下空中的防禦就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上給我停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼突然　很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不管經過多少時間都沒長進
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,相良他也已經在反省了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,相良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事　風間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然在你罰站的時候實在蠻抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,唔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}(女高中生激萌留言版　深夜巡邏老師的100日戰爭)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在某個留言版上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,從昨晚開始就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,呃...　唔..啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道是如何拍攝下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行　糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣等於是暴露行蹤給了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不過還是盡快找到犯人要他停止比較...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,喂　相良
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,什..什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了　風間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,最好還是不要讓本人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定會受傷害的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一般來說都會...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以還是盡量避免...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊　從剛才開始兩個人就鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什..什.. 什.. 什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妳就盡情的享受和過去沒有任何改變的高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不自然的太明顯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老師怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看來是藥物見效了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,繃帶已經用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下要去買了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就去把老師身體擦一擦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,能撐到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是　姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我..很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因為..又能見面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,和老師...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我..討厭那個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,妳忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.11,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這個..是妳之前說想聽的CD
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊 宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯..沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊..千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的那份報告...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,別吵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚　嗚呵..哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,呼　沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,無論如何你都要跟進去是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼我要可憐到讓你在廁所外面等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,又沒什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,問題多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯..那麼至少...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我好好的調查妳進入前的廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇啊啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哼...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這個變態...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我踩踩踩　我踩踩踩...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小要　冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哎...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的相良君有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣緊緊的黏著我實在是受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不過　總覺得很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,像什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,相良的那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就像剛進來學校的那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,喂　在幹什麼啊　你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什麼"怎麼了"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我問你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,調查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛　現在立刻住手...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,給我安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,唔...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的　不可以破壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,呀啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,哇啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不要　我的電腦啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.71,0:11:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼總是變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他們打下來的裝備嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵　是秘銀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不　也不一定是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,向南飛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那個足跡　是M9的機型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕有3臺機體啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有確切的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,空降後殲滅了高威脅性目標
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,癱瘓對空炮進行移動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,該不會是變更會合地點？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有1臺機體脫離部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,目的地是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是　對空陣地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,從這裡是沒有辦法確認的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到居然能反彈戰車炮火的直接攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能是λ-Driver  之外的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠那些不能判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是那台白色的AS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,呀　哈哈哈...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼顏色的想改都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧　白色的 AS 突破層層的包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,逃呀 逃呀 逃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀　敵人的炮火也追上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如何呀　我解說的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,咦　唔喔喔　扔掉了武器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.75,0:13:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒子彈了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然到了橋上卻受到兩岸的包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大　危　機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喔　竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,到了這裡向著水中 DIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}(DIVE=下潛)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,唔　哇啊啊啊啊啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,唉..算了　戰況差不多就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,接著　去見見客戶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今後絕對不可再發生這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我說啊..宗介
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天是怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎樣說都太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不..什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是妳多心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,呃啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不想說也沒有關係啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,呃　那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其實是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你說不要付錢..嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你們所號稱的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.31,0:14:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,高性能兵器一點用處都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才不要付錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,唔嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你媽媽沒有教過你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到可怕的人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就要保護住錢包和屁眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哼　沒什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,特別的意思啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘖...\N唔...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,唔喔喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.31,0:14:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,幹掉他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,唔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,讚　美　瑪　莉　亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:59.42,Comment,,0,0,0,,註：這是基督教讚美聖母瑪莉亞時唱的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,(唔啊啊...　呃啊啊...)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,(唔啊啊啊啊...)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,(呃呃...)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,(呃啊...　唔呃...)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,(呃啊...　呃...)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是偷拍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,在千鳥同學還沒發現之前找到犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是我建議相良君的　所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是　實在看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,無法饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,做這種事的傢伙應該天誅啊　天誅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,其實犯人還...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不　我已經有些線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,偷拍用的器材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,在更衣室的天花板上發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　那個所謂的調查是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是為了找到這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經連頻率都調查好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來只要進行逆向探查　就可以揭發犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　宗介　你真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們馬上開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,連接
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.50,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,方位090
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,距離5米
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就在隔壁的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧　突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚嗚...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚　哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是你這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,丟掉武器　舉起雙手　趴...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.18,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,喂　你是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不會考慮一下分寸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要突擊進入室內的話這是最...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,即使這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也不需要在學校的牆壁上開個大洞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,逃了呀　犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,呀　唔啊啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,讚　美　瑪　莉　亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,全部死光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不就無法收回剩下的欠款了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,唔呃　啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是你命令的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽不是常說不能怪在別人身上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,聽的到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛　死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊..這個世界究竟怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,居然充滿著殘酷的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊..我好悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,非常悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,像個白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哈啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,唔\N唔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,別..別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,在這之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,請把注意力集中到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不　要...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,呵..呵..呵呵呵呵...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你們要是敢再靠近的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把這令人噴飯的影像傳送到全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡　多麼的惡劣和無理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得你沒什麼資格說別人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明白的話　就快給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,作為一個男人這已經是最差勁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了 這是復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這是學生會長選舉中被妳打敗的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我一生都不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嘎喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,總而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把這個流傳到世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的讓妳難堪一番
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,妳好好..的品嚐一下我的怨念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只不過是單方面扭曲事實的怨恨嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,別做傻事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,唔唔...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,唔呃...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我..我說過　別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,唔　我要按了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好　我把他射殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,喂　不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧..瞧　我..我..我要按了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說只要讓那個畫面無法傳送就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　事情就簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,唔唔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,唔喔...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,唔啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,說那種話的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是這張嘴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咦　到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要打屁股了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗤　真無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退了　快點準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊　對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,妳們的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說成了魚餌呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,俺吃了一包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呀　好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你會打電話來還真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說妳們撿回老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你的消息真是靈通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的話　我還是希望妳們能安份一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這是忠告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是　這意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們沒有引起麻煩的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可以相信妳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,呀...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不..不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起　放過我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就說出實話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一直窺視著千鳥的真正目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是說和我剛說的一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然還是要裝蒜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那我只好問你的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哇啊啊啊啊啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼　首先是一根手指頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那根比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,住手　啊..啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦　可以住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對方只是個普通的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上窺視我公寓的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我所做的只有在校內啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是了不起的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是對我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,算了　已經沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是　審問仍沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,做到那種地步已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是好大的威力呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這個雷達
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我又得重買手機了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.19,0:21:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,唉　好想便便啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================NEXT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.04,0:23:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,似曾相識的敵人身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,隔絕地帶的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還有　對愛機和應該合適的機體存疑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但即使是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那也不是什麼困難的作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,下一回　迷宮與龍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.09,0:23:33.97,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1250,0)\move(810,540,796,540,0,4400])}迷宮與龍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.64,0:23:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷延長並且複雜的蜘蛛絲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,漸漸纏繞住我們的手腳
